{"id":165,"category_slug":"short-stories","category_name":"Short Stories","position":134,"title":"134. First date","subtitle":"","level":"A2","parts":41,"url":"https://dailydictation.com/exercises/short-stories/135-first-date.165/listen-and-type","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/general-english/135-first-date-2019-04-07-04-24-13/0-135-first-date.mp3","transcript":"\"Ring, ring.\" The phone is ringing.\nMy mother answers it.\n\"Hello,\" she says. It is for me.\nWhen I pick up the phone, I hear a boy's voice.\nIt is a boy I go to school with.\nThis boy is very nice, and he is cute, too.\nHe asks me if I want to go out for dinner with him tonight.\nI say yes.\nHe's going to pick me up at 5:30 p.m. in the evening.\nHe has a nice red car.\nBefore he picks me up, I have to find an outfit to wear.\nI am nervous and don't know what to wear.\nSo my sister picks out an outfit for me.\nI feel excited and have the sensation of butterflies in my stomach.\nThe inside of my hands are damp, too.\nI put on my outfit and do my hair.\nMy sister gives me some nice clips to put in my hair.\n\"Ding dong,\" the doorbell buzzes.\nMy date is here!\nI hurry to the door, so I can greet him.\nHe tells me that I look nice\nand that we are going to a place called M-T Bellies.\nWhen we arrive at M-T Bellies,\nthere is loud music playing.\nA smiling waitress comes who serves us our food.\nI order a large caesar salad.\nMy date orders steak.\nWhen it arrives, the food looks and is delicious!\nThe waitress asks us if we want dessert after we've finished.\nBut we are too full.\nSo we ask for our bill to pay.\nMy date pays for the meal.\nI brought money just in case we would share the cost.\nWhen we leave the restaurant, we go for a walk by the river.\nIt is a beautiful night.\nI am enjoying my first date.\nI am laughing and having fun.\nIt is time for us to go home.\nSo my date takes me home.\nI smile and thank him for the great time.\nI hope he'll ask me out again!","youtube_video_id":"","details_cached_at":"2026-06-15T20:56:31","challenges":[{"position":1,"content":"\"Ring, ring.\" The phone is ringing.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/general-english/135-first-date-2019-04-07-04-24-13/1.mp3","time_start":1.8,"time_end":4.59},{"position":2,"content":"My mother answers it.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/general-english/135-first-date-2019-04-07-04-24-13/2.mp3","time_start":4.84,"time_end":6.06},{"position":3,"content":"\"Hello,\" she says. It is for me.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/general-english/135-first-date-2019-04-07-04-24-13/3.mp3","time_start":6.41,"time_end":9.16},{"position":4,"content":"When I pick up the phone, I hear a boy's voice.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/general-english/135-first-date-2019-04-07-04-24-13/4.mp3","time_start":9.72,"time_end":12.76},{"position":5,"content":"It is a boy I go to school with.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/general-english/135-first-date-2019-04-07-04-24-13/5.mp3","time_start":13.03,"time_end":14.88},{"position":6,"content":"This boy is very nice, and he is cute, too.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/general-english/135-first-date-2019-04-07-04-24-13/6.mp3","time_start":15.58,"time_end":18.96},{"position":7,"content":"He asks me if I want to go out for dinner with him tonight.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/general-english/135-first-date-2019-04-07-04-24-13/7.mp3","time_start":19.69,"time_end":22.9},{"position":8,"content":"I say yes.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/general-english/135-first-date-2019-04-07-04-24-13/8.mp3","time_start":23.18,"time_end":24.48},{"position":9,"content":"He's going to pick me up at 5:30 p.m. in the evening.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/general-english/135-first-date-2019-04-07-04-24-13/9.mp3","time_start":24.76,"time_end":28.28},{"position":10,"content":"He has a nice red car.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upl